+## Duplicates And Skips
+
+- Skipped the report's restatement of the frozen recursive exact-closure rule
+  as already filed in
+  `library/factual/navier-stokes/recursive-exact-closure-must-use-the-full-active-ledger-and-exact-projected-helical-coefficients.md`.
+- Skipped the report's restatement that closure-forced spectators belong on
